"replycredit":"0","position":"611","username":"杰克史密斯","adminid":"0","groupid":"53","memberstatus":"0","number":"611","dbdateline":"1544025632","groupiconid":"11"},{"pid":"41843288","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"Nyaaarlathotep","authorid":"486183","dateline":"2018-12-6 00:01","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41843175&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">未来起航 发表于 2018-12-5 23:48</font></a><br />\r\n还有围绕的动物这个意象啊...咋给忘了<br />\r\n谢谢点破<br />\r\n不过...互相的青鸟怎样，继续讲呗 ...</div><br />\n大概都认为自己是利兹，看对方就是自己的青鸟，所以说利兹和青鸟cv是一个人也能这么理解","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"612","username":"Nyaaarlathotep","adminid":"0","groupid":"52","memberstatus":"0","number":"612","dbdateline":"1544025681","groupiconid":"10"},{"pid":"41843300","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"真红眼教授","authorid":"249963","dateline":"2018-12-6 00:02","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41843288&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">Nyaaarlathotep 发表于 2018-12-6 00:01</font></a><br />\r\n大概都认为自己是利兹，看对方就是自己的青鸟，所以说利兹和青鸟cv是一个人也能这么理解 ...</div><br />\n啊对，还有利兹青鸟的CV这么个细节","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"613","username":"真红眼教授","adminid":"0","groupid":"57","memberstatus":"0","number":"613","dbdateline":"1544025758","groupiconid":"12"},{"pid":"41843303","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"Nyaaarlathotep","authorid":"486183","dateline":"2018-12-6 00:03","message":"而且这片子开始是以女主的视角展开的，一直在暗示观众谁是利兹，谁是青鸟，其实一直他们两个人都是认为自己是利兹啊","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"614","username":"Nyaaarlathotep","adminid":"0","groupid":"52","memberstatus":"0","number":"614","dbdateline":"1544025790","groupiconid":"10"},{"pid":"41843314","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"若荼泱","authorid":"503878","dateline":"2018-12-6 00:04","message":"<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2018/12/06/5c07f6ecc0c70.png\" /></div><br />\n比翼鸟（蝈蝈PTSD幻视<br />\n<br />\n—— 来自 Google Pixel, Android 9上的 <a href=\"https://github.com/ykrank/S1-Next/releases\">S1Next-鹅版</a> v2.0.4","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"615","username":"若荼泱","adminid":"0","groupid":"52","memberstatus":"0","number":"615","dbdateline":"1544025856","groupiconid":"10"},{"pid":"41843320","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"未来起航","authorid":"467117","dateline":"2018-12-6 00:05","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41843300&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">真红眼教授 发表于 2018-12-6 00:02</font></a><br />\r\n啊对，还有利兹青鸟的CV这么个细节</div><br />\n其实吧...他俩身份换来换去，片子中间有蛮明显的提示了<br />\r\ncv这个我觉着就是加强下印象","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"616","username":"未来起航","adminid":"-1","groupid":"4","memberstatus":"0","number":"616","dbdateline":"1544025901","groupiconid":null},{"pid":"41843323","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"colohot","authorid":"436202","dateline":"2018-12-6 00:05","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41843249&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">cauchua 发表于 2018-12-5 23:57</font></a><br />\n有沒有人覺得這片不應該發生在夏季，反而是初冬或者深秋的故事</div><br />\n对，明明有亮丽的夏服，温柔的暖色调，处在最躁动年纪的主角们，整个片子却一点都感觉不到“热”","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"617","username":"colohot","adminid":"0","groupid":"49","memberstatus":"0","number":"617","dbdateline":"1544025921","groupiconid":"9"},{"pid":"41843329","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"未来起航","authorid":"467117","dateline":"2018-12-6 00:05","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41843242&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">真红眼教授 发表于 2018-12-5 23:56</font></a><br />\r\n两个人拥抱互相sekiseki的时候就是的了啊，对两个人而言对方都是自己的青鸟，最后结尾就是互相放飞对方 ...</div><br />\n是这样：我看这片一直是霙的视角，所以看起来就有点像阿宅追女神的故事<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/068.png\" />当然最后还是挺勇的，勇到希美无处逃窜（逃生门就有此意），只好接受<br />\r\n然而这是种单向的传达。希美那边我则就没有明白她对霙是什么心绪。所以没有 get到鸟儿双飞的意思。<br />\r\n最典型的：我的理解中，利兹（希美）那句“我爱你”，现实中的霙要真明白了估计会觉得特别奇怪，类似“合着我是这么重要的？”这样","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"618","username":"未来起航","adminid":"-1","groupid":"4","memberstatus":"0","number":"618","dbdateline":"1544025944","groupiconid":null},{"pid":"41843342","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"棒读","authorid":"181056","dateline":"2018-12-6 00:07","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41843288&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">Nyaaarlathotep 发表于 2018-12-6 00:01</font></a><br />\n大概都认为自己是利兹，看对方就是自己的青鸟，所以说利兹和青鸟cv是一个人也能这么理解 ...</div><br />\n这个意思其实已经很明显了，基本已经算是明示了吧<br />\n这片从本质上讲核心内涵也就是这一点<br />\n利兹与青鸟本就是一体两面，大家既是利兹也是青鸟，都有自己飞翔的天空，不必束缚对方，一起飞上天做比翼鸟，这个姿态我认为很美","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"619","username":"棒读","adminid":"0","groupid":"57","memberstatus":"0","number":"619","dbdateline":"1544026031","groupiconid":"12"},{"pid":"41843356","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"棒读","authorid":"181056","dateline":"2018-12-6 00:08","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41843323&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">colohot 发表于 2018-12-6 00:05</font></a><br />\n对，明明有亮丽的夏服，温柔的暖色调，处在最躁动年纪的主角们，整个片子却一点都感觉不到“热” ...</div><br />\n黄前久美子那对不就挺夏天的，只能说这对必须迁就真主角的时间线","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"620","username":"棒读","adminid":"0","groupid":"57","memberstatus":"0","number":"620","dbdateline":"1544026122","groupiconid":"12"},{"pid":"41843360","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"未来起航","authorid":"467117","dateline":"2018-12-6 00:09","message":"片子确实挺...长的。<br />\r\n开始时还有空慢慢找细节信息，后来不仅懒得做，还不断翻看进度条<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/005.png\" /><br />\r\n另外我倒觉得夏天就行。深秋入冬那就忒肃杀了，首先能想到的是wa之类的药味，口味不大对劲儿<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/009.gif\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"621","username":"未来起航","adminid":"-1","groupid":"4","memberstatus":"0","number":"621","dbdateline":"1544026156","groupiconid":null},{"pid":"41843371","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"Temori","authorid":"475707","dateline":"2018-12-6 00:10","message":"河豚的话大概看到以下一些<br />\r\n1.ミドリフグ（绿河豚）的一些特点：攻击性强，推荐单独养殖；饲养比较麻烦（水质，环境等）；长得很可爱，被称为天使。<br />\r\n2.希美对霙说你像利兹，向观众强化这种印象<br />\r\n3.鱼缸是学校箱庭之中的又一个鸟笼，<a href=\"http://ecrito.fever.jp/20180925221427\">彼女がフグを愛でる理由――映画『リズと青い鳥』における脚の表象と鳥かごの主題系</a>（太长没细看，可能偏离中心）<br />\r\n4.随手搜到的夏目漱石的文字：「嘘は河豚（ふぐ）汁である。その場限りで祟（たたり）がなければこれほど旨いものはない。しかし中毒（あたっ）たが最後苦しい血も吐かねばならぬ」（大意：谎言就像河豚汁，不发作是无上美味，但中毒了就吃不了兜着走）。虽然肯定不是山田的原意，我个人觉得结合河豚段也别有风味（x）。<br />\r\n5.最后附上今日沙雕：<a href=\"https://togetter.com/li/1221062\">河豚警察</a>。你京怎么能这么养河豚！<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/067.png\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"622","username":"Temori","adminid":"0","groupid":"30","memberstatus":"0","number":"622","dbdateline":"1544026224","groupiconid":"6"},{"pid":"41843379","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"杰克史密斯","authorid":"413629","dateline":"2018-12-6 00:12","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41843360&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">未来起航 发表于 2018-12-06 00:09:16</font></a><br />\n片子确实挺...长的。<br />\r\n开始时还有空慢慢找细节信息，后来不仅懒得做，还不断翻看进度条 ...</div>是说明明在夏天却完全感觉不到夏天的氛围，反而像是深秋啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/fi/app/saraba1st/id1221237470?mt=8\"><font color=\"#999999\">-- 来自 能搜索的 Stage1官方 iOS客户端</font></a>","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"623","username":"杰克史密斯","adminid":"0","groupid":"53","memberstatus":"0","number":"623","dbdateline":"1544026322","groupiconid":"11"},{"pid":"41843419","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"真红眼教授","authorid":"249963","dateline":"2018-12-6 00:16","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41843303&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">Nyaaarlathotep 发表于 2018-12-6 00:03</font></a><br />\r\n而且这片子开始是以女主的视角展开的，一直在暗示观众谁是利兹，谁是青鸟，其实一直他们两个人都是认为自己 ...</div><br />\n对，开头基本都是从霙的视角展开的，所以几乎可以说是一种误导了，让观众认为霙就是利兹，看到中途会发现希美也是利兹，最后全员利兹（？？？）","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"624","username":"真红眼教授","adminid":"0","groupid":"57","memberstatus":"0","number":"624","dbdateline":"1544026573","groupiconid":"12"},{"pid":"41843442","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"真红眼教授","authorid":"249963","dateline":"2018-12-6 00:19","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41843329&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">未来起航 发表于 2018-12-6 00:05</font></a><br />\r\n是这样：我看这片一直是霙的视角，所以看起来就有点像阿宅追女神的故事当然最后还是挺勇的，勇到希 ...</div><br />\n很简单，你把利兹=希美，利兹喂的一大群动物=希美身边的一大群学妹，青鸟=霙，青鸟可以飞上天空=霙的才能，青鸟半夜偷偷出去飞翔=霙偷偷和学妹处好关系，青鸟渴望飞上天空=霙被推荐上音大，看到中途如果把视角带入到希美这边就很好理解了，尤其是希美那一大堆小动作","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"625","username":"真红眼教授","adminid":"0","groupid":"57","memberstatus":"0","number":"625","dbdateline":"1544026770","groupiconid":"12"},{"pid":"41843453","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"若荼泱","authorid":"503878","dateline":"2018-12-6 00:20","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41839414&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">凛凛233 发表于 2018-12-5 18:02</font></a><br />\n别啊，我怎么办？<br />\r\n我还是找人学爬墙吧</div><br />\n日亚直邮的话，masadora行不行。<br />\n<br />\n—— 来自 Google Pixel, Android 9上的 <a href=\"https://github.com/ykrank/S1-Next/releases\">S1Next-鹅版</a> v2.0.4","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"626","username":"若荼泱","adminid":"0","groupid":"52","memberstatus":"0","number":"626","dbdateline":"1544026820","groupiconid":"10"},{"pid":"41843479","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"woshishen1991","authorid":"483233","dateline":"2018-12-6 00:23","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41843145&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">真红眼教授 发表于 2018-12-5 23:44</font></a><br />\r\n初看以为霙是利兹，希美是青鸟，霙追逐希美的脚步，不想希美离开<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n看到一半发现希美是利兹，霙是青鸟，绘本 ...</div><br />\n我认为在老师点破这层关系后，霙率先意识到自己是希美的青鸟，并以次确认了希美对自己的感情，于是在合奏时向希美传达出“我要自由飞翔”的信息，并表明这是自己表达爱的唯一方式，推已及人，希望希美也能自由地飞翔。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而最后直到霙表白之前，希美仍然单方面地认为自己是利兹而霙是青鸟，所以在最后一次合奏时哭是因为听到二人技术的鸿沟，意识到自己终于再也留不住她了。然而在霙表白后才发现，所谓的“音乐才能”根本不是二人感情的障碍，自己根本没必要因为这个而心怀介蒂，所以才自嘲般的笑了。既然如此，自己即使不去音大也没有关系了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更重要是的，她察觉霙已经了解了她自认为对霙的束缚，那么这种情况下霙主动飞翔的意图只一个，就是通过自己的做法来告诉希美，希望她也能自由。再加上告白来传给希美勇气，让希美知道即使她选择自由，霙对她的感情也不会有一点变化。所以后面希美把一般大学的辅导书大大方方地放在霙面前，告诉她：我也自由了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至此，二人先后意识到了双方互为对方的青鸟，然后先后向对方表明自己会自由地飞翔，解除了互相的束缚，并且互相表明了自己真切的心意（等等，希美你好像没有明说啊），所有的心结打开，二人的关系迈向了一个新的台阶。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"627","username":"woshishen1991","adminid":"0","groupid":"28","memberstatus":"0","number":"627","dbdateline":"1544027014","groupiconid":"4"},{"pid":"41843489","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"若荼泱","authorid":"503878","dateline":"2018-12-6 00:24","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41841868&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">woshishen1991 发表于 2018-12-5 21:37</font></a><br />\n即使是面对面，人和人果然也是难以互相理解的。无论是声之形，还是紫罗兰，都在强调这一点。</div><br />\n分析的真棒。<br />\n<br />\n—— 来自 Google Pixel, Android 9上的 <a href=\"https://github.com/ykrank/S1-Next/releases\">S1Next-鹅版</a> v2.0.4","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"628","username":"若荼泱","adminid":"0","groupid":"52","memberstatus":"0","number":"628","dbdateline":"1544027084","groupiconid":"10"},{"pid":"41843516","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"不是很懂二次元","authorid":"454912","dateline":"2018-12-6 00:28","message":"哇，隐喻和对照太多了，看得内心非常舒爽，整个观影过程简直是享受，结局在我看来是上扬的。<br />\r\n想吹爆，但是东西太多，词穷，就让我憋着吧<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/074.png\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"629","username":"不是很懂二次元","adminid":"0","groupid":"31","memberstatus":"0","number":"629","dbdateline":"1544027304","groupiconid":"7"},{"pid":"41843524","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"星野航","authorid":"505382","dateline":"2018-12-6 00:29","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41842640&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">vxzms 发表于 2018-12-5 14:48</font></a><br />\r\n其实amz那个有写错的，有台本的是台本数量限定版，不是初回限定版</div><br />\n听你这么一说我下意识看了一下刚刚下单的BD发现没买错orz","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"630","username":"星野航","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"630","dbdateline":"1544027353","groupiconid":"8"}],"allowpostcomment":[],"comments":[],"commentcount":[],"ppp":"30","setting_rewriterule":{"portal_topic":"topic-{name}.html","portal_article":"article-{id}-{page}.html","forum_forumdisplay":"forum-{fid}-{page}.html","forum_viewthread":"thread-{tid}-{page}-{prevpage}.html","group_group":"group-{fid}-{page}.html","home_space":"space-{user}-{value}.html","home_blog":"blog-{uid}-{blogid}.html","forum_archiver":"{action}-{value}.html","plugin":"{pluginid}-{module}.html"},"setting_rewritestatus":["portal_topic","portal_article","forum_forumdisplay","forum